root: ^Oh my grub, it’s a ship! I’m saved!
^My egg was laid here! I’ve never been anywhere else before. Please give me literally anything to do! I’m so, so bored..
^If you’ve been here your whole life, how did you learn to talk?
^From sheer boredom. I actually invented this language to talk to my many imaginary friends. I guess it just happened to already exist. There really are no completely original ideas are there?
^Please, I’ll do anything! I’ll even be your slave! I just need any form of stimuli before I completely lose my mind. Please take me with you.
